### Live Usage (as of 2018-02-23)

Any type not listed here is not used on the site.

#### `input[type="text"]`

- Honeypot fields for signup forms (hidden if JavaScript is enabled)
- Search
- Donate form

#### `input[type="email"]`

- Cluster Follow Update signup form
- Newsletter signup forms

#### `input[type="number"]`

- Donate form amount field (displayed as text field so styles don't apply)

#### `input[type="radio"]`

- Donate form frequency

#### `<fieldset>`

Fieldset should generally be used wherever multiple fields are used in a form.

- Donate form




